  [item] Provide a rationale for why the event types selected for logging are deemed to be adequate to support after-the-fact investigations of incidents; and
  [item] Review and update the event types selected for logging {{ insert: param, au-02_odp.04 }}.

[statement] Ensure that audit records contain information that establishes the following:
  [item] What type of event occurred;
  [item] When the event occurred;
  [item] Where the event occurred;
  [item] Source of the event;
  [item] Outcome of the event; and
  [item] Identity of any individuals, subjects, or objects/entities associated with the event.

[statement]
  [item] Select the appropriate assessor or assessment team for the type of assessment to be conducted;
